# O-rings
Used to seal barbed fittings on machined cell bodies, alternatively fittings could be heat-welded in place permanently after threading

---



## Specifications

|Attribute |Value|
|---|---|
|Material|FKM or similar|
|Dimensions|5mm OD, 3 mm ID|
